cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper deals with 3D registration, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of color information in the registration process also suggests the possibility of machine learning techniques (cs.MM) being used. The paper also mentions the use of point clouds, which is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the use of coherent point drift algorithm suggests the possibility of statistical learning (cs.LG) being used.
